LanguageData.Rpt_LetterDefendCall:
{0}'s settlement '{1}' is about to come under attack by {2}. Under our defense pact, they have asked us to help.

{3}

Once you arrive, the enemy will strike within 3-6 hours. Hold the town alongside its garrison to earn a reward of {4} silver and trust. Refusing or missing the deadline counts as denying aid.
